                     <interp inst="t18490611-1317-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>, feloniously uttering a forged order for 10<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., with intent to defraud <persName id="t18490611-name-571" type="victimName">
